<div id="sidebar">
    <%= render :partial => 'join_sidebar' %>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width:615px;">
    <div class="title_large_green">
        PEOPLE
    </div>
    <div class="normal">
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        <strong>People who join the Faiths At Work network are people of good will, who want to make a difference by working on common causes.</strong>
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        Inside this network, you will find Organizations that are serious about the issues they address – be they local or global.
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        Your job here is to hook up with the Organizations you like, find out what they’re doing, and provide information, content and make connections you feel are appropriate in this Network.
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        Our job is to provide you with connections and content and causes that fit your Interests.
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        You’ll get a Member Page that keeps you up-to-date with the actions and causes of all your Favorite Organizations.
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        You’ll also be able to connect with other Members whose Interests match yours.
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        We’re serious about helping Organizations that are helping the world become a better place.
        <p>
            &nbsp;
        </p>
        If that environment suits you, <%= link_to("Sign up here &raquo;", {:controller => "users", :action => "register"}) %>
    </div>
</div>
